-06-18T00:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4074e4c6eed3e246eea0fa36663487c2fb0c13ad","tid":1238514,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3445fc2819eecb264c577293ea1f3f3e655d5a","tid":1238514,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:32:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f7ff373cd674f3dd7e63a40285f321c06660d9","tid":1238514,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1091e7af4add601a0b8a50e91182a06d1cf866","tid":1238514,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"1. 仍然有5個人被控暴動罪，即係暴動的定性無變過。<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察想分化示威者，等你地以為得5個人好少就割席。<br />\n<br />\n3. 好多人用「得5個人暴動就要用咁多催淚彈」依件事嚟講笑，話嗰5個人係咪Avengers。你地已經中咗警察奸計。<br />\n而家有5個人被控暴動罪，唔等於最後只有依5個人被控暴動罪。<br />\n最終被控暴動罪的人一定唔只5個，警察睇完錄影就會搵到多啲人告。<br />\n<br />\n4. 根據《公安條例》第245章第19條：「如任何參與憑藉第18(1)條被定為非法集結的集結的人破壞社會安寧，該集結即屬暴動，而集結的人即屬集結暴動。」<br />\n即係一旦有人被控告暴動罪入咗，其他和平的人都算係參與咗暴動，只係暫時無比人告。<br />\n一日612仍然被定性為「暴動」，當日出現喺現場的人都有機會被控暴動罪（不論是否和平）。"},{"pid":"ce0cf26bec163eedd840a95cb5a4d06ce131ae7b","tid":1238514,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0eb18898b23f0a172382db740d26732cf8f5fe","tid":1238514,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T00:52:10.000Z","msg":"希望大家關注下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" cla